RP) - Non-Vested",21771,86659,"7.3",{"description":209,"appointee_id":51,"dsid":82,"endnote":7,"entity_id":210,"id":211,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":212,"income_type":213,"line_no":214,"metadata":86,"value_category_id":142,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":25,"form_type":27},"Nextera Energy, Inc. (NEE)",7798,86664,4,"Dividends","8",{"description":216,"appointee_id":51,"dsid":82,"endnote":7,"entity_id":217,"id":218,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":52,"income_type":86,"line_no":219,"metadata":86,"value_category_id":82,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":25,"form_type":27},"XPLR Infrastructure LP (XIFR - Formerly NextEra Energy Partners - NEP)",21772,86683,"9",{"description":50,"appointee_id":51,"dsid":156,"endnote":7,"entity_id":53,"id":221,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":11,"metadata":222,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":25,"form_type":27},86689,"Pursuant to the terms of my agreement with the company I received stock options as part of my compensation for my services.  At present time, I currently retain both vested and unvested stock options.  I agree that I will complete the divestiture of all of my equity in the company within 90 days of my confirmation. If I divest my vested stock options by exercising them, I will divest the resulting stock as soon as practicable but not later than 90 days after my confirmation.  Upon my confirmation and resignation from the company, all unvested stock options will be forfeited. (2021-05-01)",{"description":50,"appointee_id":51,"dsid":156,"endnote":7,"entity_id":53,"id":224,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":60,"metadata":225,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":25,"form_type":27},86688,"I will continue to participate in this health savings account. The account sponsor will not make further contributions after my separation. (2021-05-01)",{"description":227,"appointee_id":51,"dsid":156,"endnote":7,"entity_id":228,"id":229,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":66,"metadata":230,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":25,"form_type":27},"NextEra Energy, Inc. and XPLR Infrastructure LP (XIFR, formerly NextEra Energy Partners NEP)",6781,86690,"I hold unvested restricted stock and unvested restricted stock units in NextEra. I hold unvested restricted stock in XPLR. Upon my confirmation and resignation from NextEra, all unvested restricted stock and unvested restricted stock units will be forfeited  (2021-05-01)",{"description":50,"appointee_id":51,"dsid":156,"endnote":7,"entity_id":53,"id":232,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":72,"metadata":233,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":25,"form_type":27},86686,"I will continue to participate in this cash balance pension plan. The plan sponsor will not make further contributions after my separation. (2021-05-01)",{"description":50,"appointee_id":51,"dsid":156,"endnote":7,"entity_id":53,"id":235,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":78,"metadata":236,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":25,"form_type":27},86685,"I currently participate in the company’s Defined Benefit Supplemental Executive Retirement Plan (SERP), and the Defined Contribution Supplemental Retirement Plan (DCSERP) Both are cash balance accounts with no underlying holdings. My interest in both plans is unvested, and upon my confirmation and resignation from the company, I will forfeit my interest in both plans. (2021-05-01)",{"description":50,"appointee_id":51,"dsid":156,"endnote":7,"entity_id":53,"id":238,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":187,"metadata":239,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":25,"form_type":27},86687,"I will continue to participate in this defined contribution plan. The plan sponsor will not make further contributions after my separation. (2021-05-01)",{"description":241,"appointee_id":51,"dsid":156,"endnote":7,"entity_id":242,"id":243,"income_amou